# рҹӨ– Production RAG System

A complete production-grade Retrieval Augmented Generation (RAG) system with semantic search, LLM-powered answers, and a chat interface.

[![Live Demo](https://img.shields.io/badge/demo-coming_soon-yellow)]()
[![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.10+-blue)](https://www.python.org/)
[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-green)](LICENSE)

## вңЁ Features

- **рҹ“„ Document Processing**: Load and parse PDF documents
- **вңӮпёҸ Smart Chunking**: Split documents with overlap for context
- **рҹ§® Embeddings**: Generate semantic embeddings using OpenAI
- **рҹ’ҫ Vector Storage**: ChromaDB for persistent vector search
- **рҹ”Қ Semantic Retrieval**: Find relevant chunks by meaning, not keywords
- **рҹӨ– LLM Answers**: GPT-powered answers with source citations
- **рҹ’¬ Chat Interface**: Clean Streamlit UI for conversations
- **рҹ“Ҡ Metrics**: Track costs, tokens, and performance

## рҹҺҜ Progress

### вң… Day 1 - Document Processing
- [x] Environment setup
- [x] PDF document loader
- [x] Text chunking with overlap

### вң… Day 2 - Embeddings & Vector Store
- [x] OpenAI embedding generation
- [x] ChromaDB vector database
