## рҹ“Ғ Project Structure
```
production-rag-system/
в”ңв”Җв”Җ src/
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ document_loader.py      # PDF loading
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ text_chunker.py         # Text chunking
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ embeddings.py           # Embedding generation
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ vector_store.py         # ChromaDB interface
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ retriever.py            # Semantic retrieval
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ qa_generator.py         # Answer generation
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ rag_system.py           # Complete system
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ ingestion_pipeline.py   # Document ingestion
в”ңв”Җв”Җ tests/
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ test_day2.py
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ test_complete_system.py
в”ңв”Җв”Җ data/                        # Your PDF documents
в”ңв”Җв”Җ chroma_db/                   # Vector database
в”ңв”Җв”Җ app.py                       # Streamlit UI
в”ңв”Җв”Җ requirements.txt
в””в”Җв”Җ README.md
```

## рҹ§Ә Testing
```bash
# Test individual components
python src/embeddings.py
python src/vector_store.py
python src/retriever.py
python src/qa_generator.py

# Test complete system
python tests/test_complete_system.py
```

## рҹ’° Cost Estimate

**For 3-5 PDFs (~50 chunks):**
- Initial ingestion: ~$0.08
- Per query: ~$0.0005-0.001
- 100 queries: ~$0.05-0.10

**Total for development: ~$0.20-0.50**

## рҹ”§ Configuration

Edit in code or UI sidebar:
- **Model**: `gpt-3.5-turbo` (fast) or `gpt-4` (better)
- **Top K**: Number of chunks to retrieve (1-10)
- **Temperature**: 0 (focused) to 1 (creative)
- **Chunk Size**: Default 500 words
- **Chunk Overlap**: Default 50 words

